snippet.title: Natural Selection 2 'Gorilla' Trailer
snippet.description:
The Onos, marine jetpacks and new "mineshaft" map are shown for the first time in this 3 minute gameplay trailer. If you've pre-ordered, this is available for you to play right now! 

http://www.naturalselection2.com
